      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay magnesium sounds good. but i'm just really desperate because i have a huge presentation tomorrow and i know if i don't sleep tonight i'm gonna fail. if the 5mg melatonin and the ambien doesn't work, can i just take a second ambien pill? just like a one-time thing to make sure i'm out? it's not like i'll do it every night or anything.",
